  "detailed_description": "Welcome. New miner!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2735870/extras/9d6482cdaf683eaa2c8b3312eec33386.poster.avif?t=1769133458\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2735870/extras/9d6482cdaf683eaa2c8b3312eec33386.webm?t=1769133458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2735870/extras/9d6482cdaf683eaa2c8b3312eec33386.mp4?t=1769133458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Interesting underground world!</strong></h2>Different minerals and formations, underground caves and treasure maps.<br>There's a lot of interesting stuff under the ground!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2735870/extras/cf9fd93eb8342c9f01c8c3f302b1afe1.poster.avif?t=1769133458\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2735870/extras/cf9fd93eb8342c9f01c8c3f302b1afe1.webm?t=1769133458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2735870/extras/cf9fd93eb8342c9f01c8c3f302b1afe1.mp4?t=1769133458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Get stronger to explore!</strong></h2>Get closer to the 'King of Miner' rank.<br>The more powerful drill machines you upgrade to, the deeper underground you can explore!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2735870/extras/075f6288c57ff9657d0e338825827a8a.poster.avif?t=1769133458\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2735870/extras/075f6288c57ff9657d0e338825827a8a.webm?t=1769133458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2735870/extras/075f6288c57ff9657d0e338825827a8a.mp4?t=1769133458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Legendary Minerals in the Veil!</strong></h2>Find clues to the legendary minerals hidden in ancient air defenses.<br>Help the people of the underworld and you'll be one step closer to the secret.<br><br>Adventure awaits!",
